            "title": "不是石油！波斯灣國家致命資源是「水」 一旦癱瘓首都一周變死城",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"不是石油！波斯灣國家致命資源是「水」 一旦癱瘓首都一周變死城\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"466\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YfGMcY0WhXmMd83SCPBYEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ2Ng--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/79cd7f70-18f9-11f1-bfeb-396adc518216\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">不是石油！波斯灣國家致命資源是「水」 一旦癱瘓首都一周變死城</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9-%E6%B3%A2%E6%96%AF%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E8%BB%9F%E8%82%8B%E6%98%AF-%E6%B0%B4-%E6%97%A6%E7%99%B1%E7%98%93%E9%A6%96%E9%83%BD-%E5%91%A8%E8%AE%8A%E6%AD%BB%E5%9F%8E-001017972.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 09:14:36",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
